%% Upload and Analysis Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    actor Facilitator
    participant Web as Blazor Web App
    participant API as Cloud Run API
    participant GCS as Cloud Storage
    participant DB as Cloud SQL PostgreSQL
    participant PubSub as Pub/Sub
    participant Worker as Cloud Run Worker
    participant Speech as Speech-to-Text
    participant Gemini as Vertex AI Gemini
    participant Video as Video Intelligence API

    Facilitator->>Web: Upload or record session clip
    Web->>API: POST /api/v1/learning-sessions/upload
    API->>API: Validate media
    API->>GCS: Store media object
    API->>DB: Create LearningSession(status=Uploaded)
    API->>PubSub: Publish SessionUploaded event
    API-->>Web: Return sessionId + processing status

    PubSub-->>Worker: Deliver SessionUploaded event
    Worker->>DB: Mark status=Processing
    Worker->>GCS: Read media object

    alt Video file
        Worker->>Worker: Extract audio with FFmpeg
        Worker->>GCS: Store extracted audio
    end

    Worker->>Speech: Transcribe audio
    Speech-->>Worker: Timestamped transcript
    Worker->>DB: Save transcript segments

    Worker->>Gemini: Analyze transcript for learning signals
    Gemini-->>Worker: Structured JSON analysis
    Worker->>DB: Save insights and metric candidates

    opt Video analysis enabled
        Worker->>Video: Analyze video signals
        Video-->>Worker: Visual signal metadata
        Worker->>DB: Save visual signals
    end

    Worker->>Worker: Calculate session metrics
    Worker->>Gemini: Generate summary and interventions
    Gemini-->>Worker: Summary + recommendations
    Worker->>DB: Save metrics, summary, recommendations
    Worker->>DB: Mark status=Completed

    Web->>API: GET /api/v1/learning-sessions/{id}
    API->>DB: Load dashboard data
    API-->>Web: Metrics, transcript, insights, recommendations
    Web-->>Facilitator: Display dashboard
